{"tid":1034080,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友叫我陪佢去掃墓 要我自己買機票","createTime":"2019-02-23T15:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T08:18:18.000Z","uid":4187,"like":4,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"803494c3e581c427d35f454991c110bfa11fb7ae","tid":1034080,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:39:52.000Z","msg":"我男朋友提出叫我陪佢番內地一個城市掃墓 仲有佢呀公一齊 去3-4日 掃完墓以外既日子就可以飲飲食食 佢提出叫我自己比番自己既機票錢<br />\n但去到食宿會有佢親戚/朋友負責<br />\n我對於返大陸嘅興趣係麻麻地嘅 所以我唔係好想去<br />\n再加上我覺得佢叫我陪佢去掃墓 無理由叫我自己比機票<br />\n<br />\n我同佢講左之後 比佢罵我好港女<br />\n<br />\n我想問下你地覺得 我係咪應該自己比番個機票?"},{"pid":"7371a08a02264f9476be1e562fbd64fe2fd3d58a","tid":1034080,"uid":130695,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"你條仔係大陸閪? 完"},{"pid":"d5df72dcb6626144de8c09dad34b6ac70efd124a","tid":1034080,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dfc0dac9e33d4d4cdf9869ce3c352f049f17ef","tid":1034080,"uid":36402,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"唔去 有野做"},{"pid":"f346fa27a690a7b212aee6118611db6271741275","tid":1034080,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"12dfc0dac9e33d4d4cdf9869ce3c352f049f17ef","tid":1034080,"uid":36402,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"唔去 有野做"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"唔想去都唔敢開口直接講唔想去，之前試過因為要搬屋同準備轉工而唔得閒，話唔去佢媽咪餐生日飯，比佢大鬧我唔尊重佢屋企人。"},{"pid":"cc76287c448031846a9c63564a29bae76f0e23f0","tid":1034080,"uid":228213,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T15:45:09.000Z","msg":"做乜成日要人請？"},{"pid":"c02db5814ed8dcda0a5eec9e3c143e5f63e3463e","tid":1034080,"uid":36402,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f346fa27a690a7b212aee6118611db6271741275","tid":1034080,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,